<h2>Itching or burning, Mouth sores and White patches inside mouth</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms itching or burning, mouth sores and white patches inside mouth including Hay fever, Thrush (infants and children), and Coxsackie virus infection.</p>
<p>There  are 11 conditions  associated with itching or burning, mouth sores and white patches inside mouth. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
